SELECT u.username, b.biometric_data, s.security_level FROM user_data u JOIN biometric_keys b ON u.biometric_key_id = b.key_id JOIN user_security us ON u.user_id = us.user_id JOIN security_levels s ON us.level_id = s.level_id;
SELECT a.log_id, u.username, a.access_time FROM access_logs a JOIN user_data u ON a.user_id = u.user_id;

SELECT u.username, s.security_level FROM user_data u JOIN user_security us ON u.user_id = us.user_id JOIN security_levels s ON us.level_id = s.level_id WHERE s.security_level = 'High';

SELECT u.username, b.biometric_data, a.access_time FROM user_data u JOIN biometric_keys b ON u.biometric_key_id = b.key_id JOIN access_logs a ON u.user_id = a.user_id WHERE a.access_time > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
